<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Simple Dice Support</h1>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>How to Use</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Roll Dice:</strong> Tap anywhere on the screen or shake your device</li>
                <li><strong>Add Dice:</strong> Tap the "+" button (maximum 5 dice)</li>
                <li><strong>Remove Dice:</strong> Tap the "-" button (minimum 1 die)</li>
                <li><strong>Lock Dice:</strong> Tap on any die to lock it in place (it will become semi-transparent)</li>
                <li><strong>Unlock Dice:</strong> Tap on a locked die to unlock it</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Troubleshooting</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Shake to Roll Not Working:</strong> 
                    <ul>
                        <li>Ensure motion sensors are enabled in your device settings</li>
                        <li>Check if your device supports motion detection</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li><strong>Dice Not Visible:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Restart the app</li>
                        <li>Ensure you're running the latest version</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>System Requirements</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>iOS 15.0 or later</li>
                <li>Compatible with iPhone and iPad</li>
                <li>Device must support motion detection for shake feature</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="contact">
            <h2>Contact Support</h2>
            <p>If you need additional help or want to report an issue, please contact us at:</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> waylongmusk@github.com</p>
        </div>
